query:
INSERT INTO tasks (
                    responsible_user_id,
                    title,
                    start_date,
                    end_date,
                    group_id,
                    estimate,
                    category_id
                )
                VALUES (
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    $3,
                    $4,
                    $5,
                    $6,
                    $7
                )
                RETURNING
                    id as "id: TaskId"
